            <p>
                Phoenix Inspire is a Bulgarian registered non government organisation (NGO) which raises funds to create opportunities to improve the lives and prospects of disadvantaged young adults in Bulgaria.  We believe that a better and independent life is one which is based upon skills and knowledge and will which lead to employment.
                ‘Give a man a fish and you feed him for a day, teach him to fish and you feed him for a life time.’  Maimonides 
